3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20warning%20signs%20emerging%20in%20the%20labor%20market%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20says%20investors%20should%20start%20to%20consider%20adding%20riskier%20assets%20to%20their%20portfolio%20heading%20into%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20economy%20is%20in%20a%20downturn%20phase%20right%20now%20based%20on%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Regime%20Indicator%2C%20the%20economy%20could%20start%20improving%20by%20as%20early%20as%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025%2C%20the%20bank%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20note%20from%20a%20team%20of%20analysts%20led%20by%20Justin%20Post.%20That's%20thanks%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20kicking%20off%20a%20rate-cutting%20cycle%20and%20other%20encouraging%20economic%20indicators%2C%20like%20improving%20GDP%20forecasts%20and%20earnings%20estimates%2C%20as%20well%20as%20falling%20high-yield%20credit%20spreads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20in%20mind%2C%20investors%20may%20want%20to%20consider%20putting%20money%20into%20value%2C%20small-cap%2C%20and%20higher-risk%20assets%20heading%20into%202025%2C%20as%20these%20factors%20typically%20outperform%20in%20the%20recovery%20phase%20of%20the%20economic%20cycle%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222404f88c-a239-4b84-862a-9d1938a0e648%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20downturn%20to%20recovery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20the%20bank%20sees%20a%20risk-on%20outlook%20in%20the%20market%20taking%20hold%20early%20next%20year%20is%20rate%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20market%20breathed%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20when%20the%20Fed%20finally%20initiated%20an%20easing%20cycle%20with%20last%20week's%2050%20basis%20point%20rate%20cut%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rising%201.78%25%20in%20the%20two%20days%20following%20the%20policy%20adjustment.%20Bank%20of%20America%20is%20expecting%20another%2075%20basis%20points%20of%20cuts%20in%20Q4%202024%20and%20125%20basis%20points%20spread%20out%20over%20the%20course%20of%202025%2C%20bringing%20the%20terminal%20rate%20to%202.75-3.0%25%20by%20the%20end%20of%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20the%20economy%20is%20still%20in%20the%20Regime%20Indicator's%20%26quot%3Bdownturn%26quot%3B%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20downturn%20periods%2C%20investors%20usually%20flock%20to%20quality%2C%20large-cap%2C%20and%20low-risk%20companies.%20While%20Bank%20of%20America%20believes%20investors%20should%20stay%20in%20defensive%2C%20high-quality%20areas%20to%20weather%20a%20potential%20economic%20downturn%2C%20they%20should%20also%20be%20forward-looking%20in%20anticipation%20of%20improving%20conditions%20within%20the%20next%20few%20months%20by%20keeping%20their%20eye%20on%20value%2C%20small-cap%2C%20and%20higher-risk%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20screening%20for%20market%20cap%20and%20valuation%20%E2%80%94%20as%20smaller%20and%20cheaper%20companies%20tend%20to%20outperforml%20in%20an%20economic%20recovery%20%E2%80%94%20the%20analysts%20controlled%20for%20riskiness%20by%20looking%20at%20stocks%20with%20higher%20beta%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20stock's%20relative%20volatility%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20market.%20For%20example%2C%20an%20index%20like%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20a%20beta%20of%201.0%2C%20and%20each%20individual%20stock's%20beta%20is%20compared%20against%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20market.%20A%20stock%20with%20a%20beta%20above%201.0%20tends%20to%20move%20more%20than%20the%20market%20and%20vice%20versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20while%20higher-risk%20stocks%20might%20drop%20more%20dramatically%20than%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20during%20a%20downturn%2C%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20appreciate%20faster%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20market%20during%20a%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20screen%20of%20the%20three%20variables%20produced%20a%20list%20of%20a%20few%20dozen%20stocks%2C%20but%20only%20three%20were%20buy-rated%20by%20Bank%20of%20America%20analysts.%20They%20are%20listed%20below%2C%20along%20with%20their%20betas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDigital%20Turbine%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221399%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Digital%20Turbine%201%20year%20stock%20performance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2fb31cfb7f307e5747ff3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221135%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicker%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fapps-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAPPS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeta%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%203.1%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShutterstock%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221410%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shutterstock%201%20year%20stock%20performance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f21640ce3009a0fac8c3f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221174%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ETicker%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ESSTK%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EBeta%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%201.7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMagnite%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Magnite%201%20year%20stock%20performance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2fb3bd17aa3c7b2b5944e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicker%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fmgni-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMGNI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeta%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%203.3%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.