e%20also%20advises%20people%20to%20think%20about%20aesthetics%20as%20well%20as%20function%20for%20any%20item%20that%20is%20going%20to%20live%20on%20their%20countertops%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smeg.com%2Fus%2Ftoasters%5C%22%3ESmeg%20toasters%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20cheaper%20alternatives%20of%20course%2C%20but%20Smeg%20is%20a%20great%20player%20in%20the%20game%20of%20taking%20something%20that%20is%20utilitarian%20and%20making%20it%20artistic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20chrome%20Smeg%20toaster%20on%20my%20countertop%20and%20I%20love%20it.%20It's%20just%20so%20pretty%20to%20look%20at%2C%20and%20it's%20taking%20something%20so%20basic%20and%20making%20it%20elevated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBathroom%20clutter%20doesn't%20give%20your%20home%20a%20luxurious%20feel.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bathroom%20counter%20with%20makeup%20products%20on%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63fe3147b8468e001896d044%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20shouldn't%20clutter%20your%20counters.%3Cp%3EMeaghan%20Skinner%20Photography%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20fill%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbathroom-decor-ideas%5C%22%3Ebathroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20counters%20with%20products%2C%20but%20Rehman%20told%20BI%20that's%20a%20quick%20way%20to%20make%20your%20space%20feel%20cheap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPut%20your%20shit%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Rehman%20said%20plainly.%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20have%20all%20your%20products%20on%20the%20countertop.%20Especially%20if%20you're%20dealing%20with%20a%20smaller%20bathroom%2C%20that%20empty%20visual%20space%20is%20your%20friend%20that%20makes%20your%20bathroom%20feel%20high-end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20ins