t%20your%20choice%20of%20bath%20mat%20can%20actually%20make%20a%20huge%20difference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20buy%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20different%20bath%20mats%2C%20like%20the%20small%20bath%20mats%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20go%20in%20front%20of%20the%20toilet%20or%20the%20shower%20or%20the%20sink%2C%26quot%3B%20Rehman%20advised.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20try%20to%20get%20a%20large-scale%20rug%20or%20a%20large-scale%20runner%20that%20really%20creates%20this%20unified%20piece%20in%20your%20bathroom%20and%20makes%20it%20feel%20clean%20and%20simple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERehman%20knows%20some%20people%20might%20feel%20hesitant%20about%20putting%20a%20real%20rug%20in%20a%20bathroom%2C%20but%20he%20encourages%20people%20to%20remember%20there%20are%20a%20myriad%20of%20water-friendly%20materials%20rugs%20come%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20get%20a%20cool%20rug%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D57071c1cdd98adc0f3091b5416aa52200a135e56e8189db98c9db2ce4b7c3f32%26postID%3D63fd099bba7556401344c4a5%26postSlug%3Dways-youre-making-home-look-cheap-interior-designer-2023-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fruggable.com%252F%5C%22%3ERuggable%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20throw%20it%20in%20your%20washing%20machine%20every%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat%20looks%20so%20much%20better%20in%20the%20end%20than%20all%20these%20mismatched%20mats%20that%20are%20moving%20all%20over%20the%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlthough%20they're%20a%20staple%20in%20many%20homes%2C%20Rehman%20thinks%20matching%20bedroom%20sets%20look%20cheap.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223232%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pine%20wood%20bedroom%20set%20matching%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61b0d34c06b6770018c49095%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222424%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERehman%20said%20he%20is%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20matching%20bedroom%20sets.%3Cp%3EFrancois%20Lariviere%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Rehman%20told%20BI%2C%20people%20often%20think%20matching%20sets%20will%20look%20good%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-bedroom-trends-for-2023-from-interior-designers%5C%22%3Ebedrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20see%20them%20set%20up%20in%20furniture%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20so%20good%20when%20you%20walk%20into%20a%20store%2C%20and%20everything%20matches%20because%20they%20set%20it%20up%20in%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20but%20the%20second%20you%20take%20it%20home%20and%20you%20put%20it%20in%20your%20bedroom%2C%20it%20literally%20just%20looks%20like%20you%20went%20to%20a%20big%20box%20store%2C%20picked%20up%20that%20room%2C%20and%20dropped%20it%20into%20your%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Rehman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20no%20personality%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20collected%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20designer%2C%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20high-end%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20doing%20that%2C%20the%20same%20exact%20money%20that%20you're%20spending%20on%20that%2C%20spend%20it%20on%20mismatched%20pieces%20that%20are%20cohesive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERehman%20advises%20people%20to%20look%20for%20pieces%20that%20complement%20each%20other%20rather%20than%20buying%20a%20set%2C%20as%20they%20will%20make%20the%20room%20feel%20thought%20out%20and%20welcoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERehman%20also%20cautions%20people%20against%20forgetting%20to%20decorate%20their%20exteriors.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20backyard%20with%20a%20table%20and%20umbrella.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63fe31dad5d80a00182780c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20decorate%20your%20backyard.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Keeble%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption