time%20that%20show%20a%20fifth-generation%20F-35%20fighter%20armed%20with%20a%20stealthy%20long-range%20anti-ship%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20photo%2C%20released%20on%20Monday%2C%20shows%20an%20F-35C%20Lightning%20II%20carrying%20two%20AGM-158C%20Long-Range%20Anti-Ship%20Missiles%20(LRASMs)%20during%20a%20flight%20test%20conducted%20earlier%20this%20month.%20The%20aircraft%20took%20off%20from%20Naval%20Air%20Station%20Patuxent%20River%20in%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20integrate%20the%20missile%20with%20the%20carrier-based%20variant%20of%20the%20advanced%20F-35%20stealth%20fighter%20underscore%20the%20military's%20push%20to%20expand%20its%20anti-ship%20capabilities%20across%20new%20platforms.%20The%20military%20has%20acknowledged%20an%20increasing%20need%20for%20these%20capabilities%2C%20particularly%20as%20rivals%20like%20China%20strengthen%20their%20navies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20doesn't%20have%20a%20dedicated%20anti-ship%20missile%2C%20making%20the%20LRASM%20a%20valuable%20addition.%20The%20AGM-158C%20LRASM%20is%20a%20stealthy%20precision-guided%2C%20air-launched%20cruise%20missile%20that%20has%20been%20in%20service%20since%202018.%20It%20was%20developed%20to%20give%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20and%20US%20Navy%20more%20strike%20options%20in%20the%20maritime%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELRASM%20is%20the%20anti-ship%20variant%20of%20the%20AGM-158%20Joint%20Air-to-Surface%20Standoff%20Missile%20(JASSM)%20and%20can%20already%20be%20launched%20from%20Air%20Force%20B1%20bombers%20and%20Navy%20F%2FA-18%20Super%20Hornets%2C%20among%20some%20other%20aircraft.%20The%20goal%20now%20appears%20to%20be%20readying%20the%20weapon%20for%20the%20F-35%2C%20an%20increasingly%20prominent%20fifth-gen%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-35%20carrying%20the%20LRASM%20flying%20over%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f4276fce3009a0fac95770%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F-35%20seen%20carrying%20the%20LRASM%3Cp%3EUS%20military%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20ongoing%20integration%20efforts%2C%20the%20Pax%20River%20F-35%20Integrated%20Test%20Force%20(Pax%20ITF)%20team%20flew%20two%20days%20of%20test%20flights%20to%20evaluate%20flutter%2C%20loads%2C%20and%20flying%20qualities%20with%20two%20AGM-158%20loaded%20on%20external%20stations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20military%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dvidshub.net%2Fimage%2F8659318%2Fagm-158-flight-testing-begins-f-35c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20the%20caption%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20photos%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20explained%20that%20the%20Pax%20ITF%20mission%20is%20to%20carry%20out%20flight%20tests%20for%20the%20F-35B%2FC%20and%20provide%20data%20to%20support%20program%20verification%20and%20operational%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lockheedmartin.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Flockheed-martin%2Fmfc%2Fdocuments%2Fbusiness-area-landing%2FFast-Facts-LRASM.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efact%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20LRASM%2C%20the%20missile%20has%20a%20semi-autonomous%20guidance%20system%20and%20a%20range%20of%20some%20200%20nautical%20miles.%20It%20can%20deliver%20a%201%2C000-pound%20warhead%20at%20subsonic%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20its%20size%2C%20the%20F-35%20cannot%20carry%20the%20LRASM%20internally%2C%20meaning%20the%20missile%20would%20sit%20on%20the%20aircraft's%20exterior%2C%20compromising%20the%20aircraft's%20stealth%20to%20a%20certain%20degree.%20However%2C%20the%20missile%20would%20still%20give%20the%20fighter%20a%20notable%20firepower%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLRASM%20is%20a%20defined%20near-term%20solution%20for%20the%20Offensive%20Anti-Surface%20Warfare%20air-launch%20capability