20(SR)%20had%20laid%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20what%20I%20would%20describe%20as%20crisis%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BJuly's%20decline%20below%203%25%20should%20be%20sounding%20a%20very%20loud%20warning%20klaxon%20in%20the%20ears%20of%20investors%20to%20not%20forget%20what%20happened%20in%202008%20when%20the%20SR%20fell%20this%20low.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20savings%20rate%20attests%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhate-spending-consumers-economic-sentiment-retail-sales-inflation-gdp-growth-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20consumer%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20propped%20up%20the%20economy%20so%20far.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20sounds%20like%20it%20should%20be%20good%20news%2C%20but%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20the%20savings%20rate%20is%20likely%20to%20rise%20again%20after%20plummeting%20to%20such%20low%20levels.%20Forecasters%20have%20argued%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-outlook-hard-landing-economy-consumer-spending-slowdown-growth-gdp-2024-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DConsumers%2520are%2520finally%2520slowing%2520their%2Cand%2520a%2520weakening%2520job%2520market.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomy%20could%20experience%20a%20slowdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20once%20consumers%20pull%20back%20on%20their%20spending%20and%20begin%20to%20build%20their%20savings%20again.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20what%20happened%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%2C%20when%20an%20uptick%20in%20the%20savings%20rate%20preceded%20the%20recession%2C%20Edwards%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20households%20aren't%20nearly%20as%20indebted%20as%20they%20were%20during%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20Americans%20are%20still%20showing%20signs%20of%20financial%20strain.%20Two-thirds%20of%20middle-income%20households%20said%20they%20believed%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.primerica.com%2Fpublic%2FFact_Sheet_Prime