m-altman-announcement-chatgpt-news-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT's%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20at%20its%20Spring%20Update%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20voice%20feature%20powered%20by%20GPT-4o%20was%20eerily%20human-like%2C%20borderline%20flirty%2C%20and%20gave%20a%20glimpse%20into%20what%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20chatbots%20could%20look%20like.%20The%20feature%20offers%20users%20natural%2C%20real-time%20conversations%20that%20you%20can%20interrupt%20anytime.%20It%20also%20senses%20and%20responds%20to%20your%20emotions%2C%20according%20to%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20months%20of%20anticipation%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscarlett-johansson-openai-voice-dispute-may-regret-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20Scarlet%20Johanson%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20OpenAI%20finally%20started%20rolling%20out%20its%20highly%20anticipated%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20to%20ChatGPT%20Plus%20and%20Team%20users%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt'll%20also%20start%20offering%20the%20feature%20to%20Enterprise%20and%20Edu%20users%20next%20week%2C%20although%20it's%20not%20available%20yet%20for%20the%20EU%2C%20UK%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Iceland%2C%20Norway%2C%20and%20Liechtenstein%2C%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20will%20also%20release%20five%20new%20voices%20to%20Standard%20and%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20four%20already%20available.%20You'll%20know%20you%20have%20access%20to%20the%20new%20feature%20once%20you%20see%20a%20pop-up%20message%20next%20to%20the%20entry%20point%20to%20Voice%20Mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20trying%20out%20the%20alpha%20version%20of%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20so%20here's%20what%20you%20can%20expect%20once%20you%20get%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22884feeb9-92dc-4ee4-9766-d24083afec11%5C%22%3EIt's%20highly%20entertaining%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20get%20old%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20it%20hasn't%20yet%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20interrupt%20the%20chatbot%20mid-response%20was%20an%20oddly%20satisfying%20experience%20that%20made%20me%20feel%20in%20control.%20It%20also%20took%20out%20the%20frustration%20of%20having%20to%20go%20back%20and%20forth%20with%20a%20virtual%20assistant%20that%20didn't%20hear%20me%20right%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20got%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20pulling%20up%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20in%20front%20of%20others%20and%20watching%20their%20jaws%20drop%20when%20it%20responds.%20It's%20slightly%20eerie%20how%20human%20it%20sounds%2C%20but%20also%20incredibly%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20intonation%20is%20close%20to%20flawless%2C%20and%20everything%20from%20its%20thoughtful%20pauses%20to%20laughing%20at%20its%20own%20jokes%20creates%20a%20surreal%20experience.%20To%20test%20its%20understanding%20of%20more%20complex%20topics%2C%20I%20gave%20it%20sample%20SAT%20questions%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-4o-real-time-feedback-coding-math-demo-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easked%20it%20to%20choose%20the%20right%20answer.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20took%20on%20the%20role%20of%20a%20tutor%20and%20guided%20me%20through%20the%20solutions%2C%20step%20by%20step%20%E2%80%94%20and%20getting%20the%20answers%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20mainly%20stuck%20with%20the%20Breeze%20voice%2C%20the%20diverse%20options%20of%20voices%20provided%20a%20glimpse%20into%20how%20people%20can%20personalize%20their%20experience.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20understood%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freplika-ai-girlfriend-boyfriend-online-dating-companion-age-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20can%20use%20AI%20as%20a%20companion.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfa300c6-9af1-4914-89ed-0335508299d2%5C%22%3EThe%20response%20accuracy%20isn't%20quite%20there%20yet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20of%20the%20individual%20responses%20I%20received%20from%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20were%20accurate%20and%20helpful%2C%20my%20overall%20conversations%20were%20less%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chatbot%20would%20sometimes%20stop%20listening%20to%20my%20voice%20or%20start%20late.%20An%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20used%20learnings%20from%20the%20alpha%20version%20to%20improve%20conversation%20speed%20and%20smoothness.%20So%20some%20of%20those%20lapses%20may%20be%20fixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvanced%20Voice%20Mode%20also%20didn't%20give%20the%20thoroughness%20or%20detail%20that%20the%20text%20mode%20offers.%20There%20were%20also%20some%20instances%20where%20the%20conversation%20went%20in%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20asked%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20to%20recommend%20the%20best%20credit%20card%20reward%20program%20for%20me%2C%20but%20it%20got%20sidetracked%20into%20a%20conversation%20about%20my%20hobbies.%20It%20eventually%20suggested%20American%20Express%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20redirect%20the%20conversation%20multiple%20times%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20offer%20much%20detail%20about%20the%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT's%20Advanced%20Voice%20Mode%20feels%20a%20world%20apart%20from%20Siri%20or%20other%20voice%20assistants%2C%20which%20don't%20offer%20smooth%20back-and-forth%20conversations%20or%20pick%20up%20on%20emotion.%20But%20it's%20not%20quite%20up%20to%20speed%20with%20the%20text%20version%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-advanced-voice-mode-heres-what-to-expect-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727277691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f42ac9ce3009a0fac958c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F