hat%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-common-mistakes-for-balanced-blood-sugar-dietitian-tips-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblood%20sugar%20was%20crashing%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20afternoon%20when%20she%20had%20a%20high-carb%20breakfast%2C%20which%20helped%20explain%20the%20exhaustion%20she'd%20been%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20little%20planning%20ahead%2C%20she's%20been%20able%20to%20adjust%20her%20habits%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhabits-for-healthy-blood-sugar-levels-doctor-advice-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20stable%20blood%20sugar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20better%20energy%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20finding%20habits%20that%20work%20best%20for%20her%20body%2C%20routine%2C%20and%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20guidance%20that's%20kind%20of%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20doesn't%20necessarily%20optimize%20for%20the%20best%20diet%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Berry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22193ddea8-2a04-432a-9855-89e3bb6f66db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlood%20sugar%20spikes%20and%20dips%20may%20mess%20with%20your%20energy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBerry%20said%20she%20is%20what's%20known%20in%20ZOE%20studies%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdipper%2C%26quot%3B%20prone%20to%20blood%20sugar%20crashes%20that%20can%20leave%20her%20feeling%20foggy%20and%20wanting%20to%20snack%20in%20search%20of%20more%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2025-30%25%20of%20people%20fall%20into%20this%20category%2C%20tending%20to%20experience%20drops%20in%20blood%20sugar%20below%20baseline%20several%20hours%20after%20eating%20a%20lot%20of%20carbs%2C%20ZOE%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df7cc91ff7515aef509e388dd08863179d0c1373d73e48ba15dd3ed1259cb220b%26postID%3D66f2e247d8616474984c9868%26postSlug%3Dnutrition-researcher-eat-to-avoid-afternoon-crash-blood-sugar-2024-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.