C%20we%20may%20unlock%20a%20critical%20pathway%20to%20driving%20meaningful%20change%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FMaster%20of%20Stocks)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAddressing%20stereotypes%20and%20encouraging%20men%20to%20view%20family%20planning%20as%20a%20shared%20responsibility%20requires%20a%20comprehensive%20approach.%20Public%20health%20systems%2C%20family%20planning%20programmes%2C%20and%20communication%20strategies%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20promote%20male%20involvement%20actively.%20By%20engaging%20men%20as%20equal%20partners%20in%20family%20planning%2C%20we%20may%20unlock%20a%20critical%20pathway%20to%20driving%20meaningful%20change%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20argues%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20sustained%20effort%20in%20behaviour%20change%20communication%2C%20combined%20with%20active%20on-ground%20engagement%20with%20men%2C%20is%20essential%20while%20promoting%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20and%20decision-making%20autonomy.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20shifting%20mindsets%20and%20addressing%20stereotypes%20to%20empower%20women%20in%20making%20informed%20health%20decisions%2C%20while%20also%20fostering%20open%20communication%20between%20spouses.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20initiate%20these%20efforts%20early%20by%20engaging%20adolescents%20in%20discussions%20about%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20and%20rights.%20Additionally%2C%20strategic%20engagement%20is%20needed%20to%20encourage%20men%20to%20consider%20vasectomy%20as%20a%20viable%20family%20planning%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20get%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20male%20engagement%20intervention%20needs%20a%20multi-sectoral%20approach.%20Education%2C%20age%20at%20marriage%2C%20health-seeking%20behaviour%2C%20and%20socio-cultural%20norms%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20simultaneously%20and%20concurrently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20two%20steps%20she%20recommends%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrontline%20health%20workers%20(ASHAs%2C%20ANMs)%20must%20be%20supported%20and%20male%20health%20workers%20must%20be%20added%20to%20supplement%20the%20existing%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiven%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20present%20emphasis%20on%20strengthening%20counselling%20at%20hospitals%2C%20an%20increased%20thrust%20on%20couples%20counselling%20and%20follow-ups%20is%20likely%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%20is%20the%20right%20solution%20for%20couples%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367538%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FIndianFaces%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%E2%80%99s%20effort%20to%20engage%20male%20peer%20educators%20as%20part%20of%20the%20RKSK%20(Rashtriya%20Kishor%20Swasthya%20Karyakram)%20programme%20is%20a%20move%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLastly%2C%20the%20involvement%20of%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20private%20partners%2C%20to%20involve%20men%20in%20this%20process%20needs%20to%20be%20underlined.%20Innovative%20ways%20to%20ensure%20this%20under%20existing%20PPP%20(public-private%20partnership)%20and%20social%20franchising%20models%20will%20positively%20impact%20health%20and%20family%20planning%20at%20the%20community%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20male%20participation%20crucial%20in%20family%20planning%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20believes%20that%20if%20you%20already%20have%20a%20child%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20intend%20to%20have%20another%2C%20getting%20a%20vasectomy%20is%20a%20must%20so%20that%20you%20can%20move%20on%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20have%20children%20at%20all%2C%20my%20suggestion%20is%20to%20take%2018%20months%20as%20a%20couple%20to%20discuss%20this%20in%20honest%20detail%2C%20do%20the%20research%2C%20talk%20to%20experts%2C%20understand%20what%20it%20is%20to%20be%20a%20parent%20and%20have%20those%20delicate%20conversations%20with%20your%20family.%20Once%20you%20are%20clear%20about%20this%20decision%2C%20get%20the%20procedure%20done%20and%20move%20on%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20Poonam%20notes%20that%20the%20discourse%20on%20the%20engagement%20of%20men%20as%20partners%20in%20accessing%20family%20planning%20and%20health%20services%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20contraceptive%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMale%20participation%20is%20about%20being%20responsible%20and%20respecting%20equality%20rather%20than%20just%20about%20decision-making.%20It%20should%20extend%20to%20the%20role%20of%20men%20as%20enablers%20and%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ensuring%20dignity%2C%20equal%20voice%2C%20and%20reproductive%20rights%20for%20women.%20Male%20participation%20should%20not%20mean%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20decision-making%20powers%20are%20encumbered%2C%20and%20women%20are%20forced%20to%20accept%20men%E2%80%99s%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudies%20reveal%20that%20men%20often%20control%20contraception%20decision-making%20and%20decision%20of%20contraception%20of%20female%20partners%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20prevalence%20of%20intimate%20partner%20violence%2C%20which%20can%20impede%20contraceptive%20use%20as%20well%20as%20increase%20the%20risk%20for%20contraceptive%20failure.%20Male%20engagement%20in%20family%20planning%20should%20improve%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20reproductive%20health%20and%20promote%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727275238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Mumbai-based%20couple%20chose%20a%20vasectomy%20after%20deciding%20not%20to%20have%20children%2C%20breaking%20societal%20norms.%20Their%20decision%20came%20after%20extensive%20discussions%2C%20research%2C%20and%20consultations%20with%20doctors.%20Highlighting%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20procedure%20and%20societal%20challenges%2C%20they%20advocate%20for%20more%20men%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20family%20planning%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367509%2Fworld-contraception-day-why-more-indian-men-should-get-vasectomy-family-planning%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kareena%20Kapoor%20on%20'Chameli'%3A%20'It%20was%20a%20brave%20film'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727275135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113672716%2Cimgsize-30500.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-says-chameli-was-a-brave-film-to-do-it-was-just-a-sense-of-freedom%2Farticleshow%2F113672716.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113672716.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ECelebrating%2025%20years%20in%20cinema%2C%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20opens%20up%20about%20her%20role%20in%20the%202004%20film%20'Chameli'.%20She%20was%20motivated%20to%20take%20on%20the%20challenging%20character%20of%20a%20prostitute%20due%20to%20her%20grandfather%20Raj%20Kapoor's%20similar%20work.%20%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20something%20that%20I%20took%20to%20instantly%20because%20when%20I%20was%20narrated%20the%20subject%2C%20it%20was%20a%20story%20of%20one%20night%20and%20my%20grandfather%20Raj%20Kapoor%20had%20also%20done%20a%20story%20of%20a%20film%20which%20was%20about%20one%20night%2C%20which%20was%20%E2%80%98Jaagti%20Raho%E2%80%99%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20She%20also%20recalls%20how%20the%20film's%20songs%20became%20hits%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20her%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkareena-kapoor-khan-says-chameli-was-a-brave-film-to-do-it-was-just-a-sense-of-freedom%2Farticleshow%2F113672716.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin's%20'Top%20Secret'%20Meet%20Over%20Nukes%20As%20Ukraine%20Plans%20Cruise%20Missile%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20called%20for%20an%20urgent%20meeting%20of%20Moscow's%20top%20security%20council%20to%20discuss%20its%20nuclear%20deterrence.%20The%20move%20comes%20amid%20rising%20concerns%20in%20Russia%20over%20Ukraine%20being%20allowed%20by%20Western%20powers%20to%20use%20cruise%20missiles%20to%20target%20locations%20deep%20inside%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20UK%20reportedly%20cleared%20the%20use%20of%20its%20'Storm%20Shadow'%20cruise%20missile%20to%20be%20used%20to%20bomb%20Russia.%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20even%20flew%20to%20Washington%20DC%20to%20meet%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20two%20leaders%20reportedly%20discussed%20Ukraine's%20use%20of%20weapons%20on%20Russian%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20intelligence%20had%20information%20about%20such%20a%20possibility%20and%20had%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20necessary%20for%20Moscow%20to%20revise%20its%20nuclear%20doctrine%20because%20of%20the%20West's%20escalation%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fdvsfo8vg_storm-shadow-long-range-missiles_625x300_13_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKremlin%20spokesperson%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20said%20that%20Mr%20Putin%20will%20meet%20the%20most%20powerful%20officials%20in%20his%20administration%20to%20discuss%20the%20war%20strategy%20going%20forward.%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20a%20speech%20by%20the%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Peskov%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20rest%2C%20for%20obvious%20reasons%2C%20will%20be%20marked%20'top%20secret'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20reports%20that%20the%20United%20States%20and%20United%20Kingdom%20are%20about%20to%20give%20clearance%20to%20Ukraine%20for%20Kyiv%20to%20launch%20cruise%20missiles%20on%20Russian%20soil%2C%20President%20Putin%20said%20this%20month%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20West%20would%20be%20directly%20fighting%20with%20Russia%20if%20it%20gave%20such%20permission%20to%20Ukraine%20(to%20bomb%20Russia)%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20Moscow%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20decisions%26quot%3B%20in%20such%20a%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERUSSIA'S%20NUCLEAR%20DOCTRINE%20%26amp%3B%20TREATY%20WITH%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20nuclear%20power.%20Together%2C%20Russia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20control%2088%25%20of%20the%20world's%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20current%20nuclear%20doctrine%20was%20set%20in%20place%20by%20Vladimir%20Putin%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20before%20the%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20broke%20out.%20According%20to%20the%20current%20doctrine%2C%20Russia%20may%20use%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20the%20scenario%20where%20it%20comes%20under%20a%20nuclear%20attack%20or%20if%20a%20conventional%20attack%20threatens%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fim09u9j8_russian-yars-intercontinental-ballistic-missile-system-reuters_625x300_25_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Putin%2C%20who%20is%20the%20primary%20decision%20maker%20on%20Russia's%20massive%20nuclear%20arsenal%2C%20is%20now%20planning%20how%20to%20respond%20if%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20European%20allies%20allow%20Ukraine%20to%20use%20Western-supplied%20missiles%20to%20strike%20deep%20inside%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20have%20a%20nuclear%20treaty%20called%20the%20US-Russia%20New%20START%20Treaty%2C%20which%20entered%20into%20force%20on%20February%205%2C%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20treaty%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20had%20seven%20years%20to%20meet%20the%20treaty's%20central%20limits%20on%20strategic%20offensive%20arms%20(by%20February%205%2C%202018)%20and%20are%20then%20obligated%20to%20maintain%20those%20limits%20for%20as%20long%20as%20the%20treaty%20remains%20in%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20State%20Department%2C%20this%20treaty%20enhances%20US%20national%20security%20by%20placing%20verifiable%20limits%20on%20all%20Russian%20deployed%20intercontinental-range%20nuclear%20weapons.%20The%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20have%20agreed%20to%20extend%20the%20treaty%20through%20February%204%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fj4c9ihng_us-medium-range-ballistic-missile-launch-test-reuters_625x300_25_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20said%20that%20any%20discussions%20about%20a%20replacement%20to%20the%20US-Russia%20New%20START%20Treaty%2C%20which%20expires%20in%202026%2C%20would%20need%20to%20take%20into%20account%20European%20nuclear%20potential%20-%20shorthand%20for%20the%20arsenals%20of%20Britain%20and%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20yet%20received%20a%20response%20from%20the%20Americans%20to%20this%2C%20but%20of%20course%20an%20agreement%20is%20needed%20and%20negotiations%20should%20begin%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Peskov%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20a%20possible%20replacement%20for%20the%20New%20START%20Treaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20STORM%20SHADOW%20MISSILE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20already%20has%20the%20UK-supplied%20Storm%20Shadow%20missile%2C%20but%20uses%20it%20only%20within%20its%20territory%20to%20combat%20Russian%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20there%20are%20restriction%20on%20Ukraine%20on%20the%20use%20of%20advanced%20western%20weaponry%20on%20targets%20within%20the%20Russian%20territory%2C%20but%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20change%20with%20clearances%20reportedly%20being%20issued%20by%20the%20UK%2C%20with%20US%20backing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fdit2seng_storm-shadow-missile-ukraine_625x300_12_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Storm%20Shadow%20is%20a%20low-observable%2C%20long-range%20air-launched%20cruise%20missile.%20It%20is%20jointly%20developed%20by%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20France%20and%20has%20a%20range%20of%20around%20500%20km.%20It%20has%20already%20been%20integrated%20into%20Ukrainian%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20including%20the%20Russia-built%20Su-24%20bombers%20-%20a%20legacy%20of%20the%20past%2C%20from%20when%20Ukraine%20was%20part%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Soviet%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Storm%20Shadow%20missile%20has%20a%20range%20of%20around%20500%20km%20and%20can%20target%20territories%20deep%20inside%20Russia.%20(Photo%20Credit%3A%20Posted%20on%20X%20by%20%40TopLeadEU)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Storm%20Shadow%20missile%20has%20a%20range%20of%20around%20500%20km%20and%20can%20target%20territories%20deep%20inside%20Russia.%20(Photo%20Credit%3A%20Posted%20on%20X%20by%20%40TopLeadEU)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fn8jnums4_ukraine-s