e%20queues%20to%20donate%20blood.%20Some%20people%20are%20even%20saying%20that%20they%20have%20two%20eyes%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20donate%20one%20or%20they%20have%20two%20kidneys%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20donate%20one.%20That%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20spirit%20we%20are%20seeing.%20There%20is%20a%20passion%20and%20enthusiasm%20in%20this%20community.%20Such%20a%20people%20can%20never%20lose%20to%20any%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Israeli%20envoy%20to%20India%20Reuven%20Azar%20said%20most%20of%20the%201%2C700%20military%20targets%20that%20Israel%20targeted%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20in%20the%20past%2048%20hours%20were%20%26quot%3Bembedded%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20civilians%20and%20the%20families%20did%20not%20evacuate%20on%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(This%20was)%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20called%20them%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20we%20intercepted%20radio%20communications...%20we%20tried%20every%20way%20possible%20to%20take%20them%20out%20of%20harm's%20way.%20Despite%20that%2C%20%C2%A0yes%2C%20there%20were%20some%20civilians%20that%20were%20killed%20as%20well.%20But%20when%20you%20look%20at%20the%20magnitude%20of%20this%20-%201%2C700%20military%20targets%20in%2048%20hours%20-%20you%20will%20see%20that%2C%20actually%2C%20this%20has%20been%20very%20successful%3B%20because%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20when%20you%20compare%20the%20damage%20that%20would%20be%20caused%20from%20these%20missiles%20to%20Israeli%20civilians%20to%20the%20price%20that%20the%20people%20have%20to%20pay%2C%20it's%20a%20relatively%20low%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azar%20said%20every%20loss%20of%20life%20is%20tragic%20and%20claimed%20that%20Israel%20does%20whatever%20is%20possible%20to%20take%20civilians%20out%20of%20harm's%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E23%20More%20Killed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon%20said%2023%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20several%20injured%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20third%20day%20of%20major%20Israeli%20strikes.%20Hezbollah%20has%20said%20it%20fired%20a%20ballistic%20missile%20that%20reached%20the%20key%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Tel%20Aviv%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20before%20being%20intercepted%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20also%20said%20it%20is%20calling%20up%20two%20reserve%20brigades%20to%20its%20northern%20border.%20%26quot%3BThe%20IDF%20(Israel%20Defense%20Forces)%20is%20calling%20up%20two%20reserve%20brigades%20for%20operational%20missions%20in%20the%20northern%20arena...%20to%20enable%20the%20continuation%20of%20combat%20against%20the%20Hezbollah%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727273040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F2r29dlqo_lebanon-strikes-afp_625x300_24_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-some-areas-no-city-or-village-spared-lebanese-witness-on-israel-strikes-6648269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20city%20or%20village%20in%20certain%20areas%20has%20been%20spared%20in%20the%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20Lebanon%20in%20which%20over%20500%20civilians%2C%20including%2050%20children%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Beirut%20has%20told%20NDTV%2C%20claiming%20that%20citizens%20are%20standing%20with%20Hezbollah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-some-areas-no-city-or-village-spared-lebanese-witness-on-israel-strikes-6648269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Andhra%20Says%20Rs%20600%20Crore%20Flood%20Compensation%20Paid%20In%20Record%20Time%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20devastating%20floods%20struck%20Vijayawada%20and%20nearby%20areas%20in%20September%2C%20over%20four%20lakh%20households%20were%20affected.%20These%20areas%20could%20not%20be%20accessed%20till%20September%2010%20and%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20start%20any%20enumeration%20activities%20for%20compensation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20immediately%20after%20the%20water%20receded%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20set%20about%20the%20challenging%20task%20of%20enumeration%20and%20managing%20the%20compensation%20disbursement%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20tech-based%20solution%20was%20designed%20with%20a%20front-end%20app%20and%20a%20back-end%20database%20operating%20on%20a%20hand-held%20device%20that%20could%20manage%20the%20enumeration%20process.%20This%20handheld%20device%20was%20given%20to%20the%20enumeration%20teams%2C%20who%20then%20went%20into%20the%20field%20and%20started%20the%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESome%201%2C600%20teams%20went%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%20and%20the%20entire%20enumeration%20was%20completed%20in%20three%20days.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20enumeration%2C%20no%20bank%20account%20data%20was%20collected.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20government%20said%20Aadhaar%20data%20was%20collected%2C%20and%20this%20was%20used%20to%20reach%20the%20validated%20bank%20account%20details%20of%20each%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20September%2022%2C%20which%20was%20a%20Sunday%2C%20the%20list%20of%20proposed%20beneficiaries%20was%20put%20up%20so%20that%20they%20could%20seek%20changes%20or%20register%20complaints.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20September%2024%2C%20at%20least%20Rs%20602%20crore%20was%20transferred%20to%20an%20online%20gateway.%20The%20bank%20account%20data%20of%20four%20lakh%20households%20was%20also%20integrated%20through%20the%20UPI%20portal%20so%20that%20the%20payments%20could%20be%20made%20instantly.%20In%20comparison%2C%20the%20compensation%20amount%20is%20in%20far%20excess%20of%20the%20NDRF%20norms%20prescribed%2C%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EToday%2C%20the%20disbursements%20are%20being%20successfully%20transferred%2C%20within%20a%20timeline%20of%20just%2015%20days%20from%20the%20date%20of%20the%20floods.%20This%20is%20the%20fastest%20timeline%20for%20compensation%20disbursement%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20successfully%20able%20to%20achieve%20this%2C%20the%20state%20government%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20when%20the%20previous%20government%20led%20by%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20managed%20the%20compensation%20process%20for%20Michuang%20cyclone%2C%20which%20struck%20on%20December%201%2C%202023%2C%20the%20compensation%20of%20Rs%20442%20crores%20was%20disbursed%20on%20May%2017%2C%202024%2C%20or%20over%20five%20months%20since%20the%20natural%20disaster%20struck.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20we%20were%20motivated%20to%20provide%20immediate%20and%20sufficient%20compensation.%20Our%20Chief%20Minister%20led%20by%20example%20during%20the%20relief%20efforts.%20We%20are%20happy%20about%20this%20unprecedented%20speed%20in%20disbursing%20the%20compensation%20amounts.%20We%20hope%20our%20efforts%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20successful%20template%20for%20future%20disaster%20management%20initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20RP%20Sisodia%2C%20Special%20Chief%20Secretary%20(Revenue).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727273040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fovrksemg_chandrababu-naidu_625x300_11_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fandhra-pradesh-news%2Fandhra-claims-rs-600-crore-flood-compensation-paid-in-record-time-10-points-6648264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20gave%20Rs%20602%20crore%20compensation%20to%20four%20lakh%20beneficiaries%20in%20a%20record%20time%20of%2015%20days%20using%20technology-driven%20interventions%2C%20the%20government%20s