%20public%20health%20system%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727269620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fijglfd0g_abortion-representational_625x300_15_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-korean-vlogger-claims-to-have-aborted-baby-at-9-months-probe-underway-6647828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20South%20Korean%20vlogger%20has%20courted%20controversy%20after%20claiming%20that%20she%20terminated%20her%20pregnancy%20at%20nine%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-korean-vlogger-claims-to-have-aborted-baby-at-9-months-probe-underway-6647828%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222024%20Mahindra%20Thar%20Roxx%204x4%20Prices%20Revealed%3A%20Check%20Variant-Wise%20Pricing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahindra%20Thar%20Roxx%20was%20recently%20launched%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20it%20is%20enjoying%20strong%20attention%20from%20the%20off-roading%20community.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20brand%20had%20been%20tight-lipped%20about%20the%20prices%20of%20the%204x4%20variants%20until%20now.%20However%2C%20the%20prices%20are%20now%20revealed%2C%20with%20an%20introductory%20starting%20price%20of%20Rs%2018.79%20lakh%20(ex-showroom)%20for%20the%204x4%20trims.%20The%204x4%20configuration%20is%20offered%20exclusively%20with%20the%20diesel%20engine%20that%20puts%20out%20a%20peak%20power%20output%20of%20152%20Hp%20and%20330%20Nm%20with%20a%20manual%20gearbox%20and%20175%20Hp%20against%20370%20Nm%20with%20a%20torque%20converter%20automatic%20gearbox.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQqSfjUfiZmQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Mahindra%20Thar%20Roxx%20Review%20%7C%20NDTV%20Auto%20%7C%20Why%20