omments%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20authorised%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Ranaut%20retracted%20her%20remarks%20and%20issued%20an%20apology.%20She%20added%20that%20moving%20forward%2C%20she%20will%20ensure%20her%20views%20align%20with%20the%20party's%20stance%20rather%20than%20representing%20her%20personal%20opinions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20national%20spokesperson%20Jaiveer%20Shergill%20further%20said%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20bond%20with%20Punjab%2C%20the%20farmers%20of%20Punjab%20and%20%26quot%3BPunjabiyat%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20unbreakable%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20said%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20doubt%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20bond%20with%20Punjab%2C%20the%20farmer%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Punjabiyat%20is%20an%20unbreakable%2C%20unshakable%20bond%20and%20that%20bond%20should%20not%20be%20judged%20or%20seen%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20irresponsible%20comments%20being%20made%20by%20one%20MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20national%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20BJP%20Spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20has%20said%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20remarks%20are%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20statements%26quot%3B%20and%20don't%20depict%20the%20BJP's%20view%20on%20farm%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20statement%20on%20the%20farm%20bills%20that%20were%20withdrawn%20by%20central%20govt%2C%20is%20going%20viral.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20this%20statement%20is%20a%20personal%20statement%20by%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhatia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727268300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fqut2q7go_jaiveer-shergill-kangana-ranaut_625x300_25_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nd