ext%20couple%20of%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20so%20dire%20that%20a%20group%20of%20engineers%20spent%20considerable%20time%20at%20the%20Balcony%20C%20stand%20and%20warned%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20(UPCA)%20to%20close%20it%20during%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20stand%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20take%20the%20weight%20of%20even%2050%20fans%2C%20if%20they%20start%20jumping%20after%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rishabh%20Pant%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107048-rishabh-pant-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERishabh%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20hits%20a%20six.%20This%20part%20of%20the%20stadium%20is%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20repair%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20a%20PWD%20engineer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20Pant%20returned%20to%20the%20international%20Tests%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20series%20post%20his%20recovery%20after%20a%20serious%20car%20accident%20and%20immediately%20stamped%20his%20class.%20His%20brisk%20scores%20in%20India's%20first%20match%20of%20the%20series%2C%20including%20a%20century%20in%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20has%20brought%20him%20back%20to%20ICC%20Test%20rankings%20and%20he%20is%20in%20sixth%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%2010%20rankings%20in%20Tests%20released%20by%20ICC%20in%20Tests%20and%20ODIs%20saw%20ups%20and%20downs%20after%20some%20intense%20international%20cricket%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20(751)%20has%20moved%20to%20fifth%20rankings%2C%20also%20helped%20by%20half-century%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20match.%20Pant%20is%20behind%20him%20at%20731%20rating%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofil