aidu%20of%20making%20the%20allegation%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20motive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20animal%20fat%20adulteration%20did%20not%20occur%2C%20he%20intentionally%20lied%20that%20it%20happened%20and%20falsely%20propagated%20that%20devotees%20ate%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20reprimand%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20key%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20said%20the%20tanker%20containing%20the%20possibly%20adulterated%20ghee%20arrived%20at%20Tirupati%20on%20July%2012%2C%20but%20was%20rejected%20and%20not%20used%20to%20prepare%20prasadams.%20%26quot%3BThe%20robust%20practices%20in%20place%20for%20decades%20in%20TTD%20could%20identify%20the%20questionable%20quality%20and%20therefore%20the%20ghee%20was%20not%20used.%20Despite%20this%20comforting%20scenario%2C%20Mr.%20Naidu%20chose%20to%20callously%20make%20a%20remark%20that%20Tirumala%20Laddus%20were%20made%20with%20animal%20fats%20and%20not%20with%20ghee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP%20leader%20said%20Mr%20Naidu%20had%2C%20in%20%26quot%3Btotal%20disregard%20to%20strong%20religious%20sentiments%20and%20with%20the%20malafide%20intent%20to%20spread%20lies%26quot%3B%2C%20brought%20the%20issue%20to%20light%20in%20a%20political%20party%20meeting%20on%20September%2018%2C%20more%20than%20two%20months%20after%20the%20tanker%20was%20rejected.%20%26quot%3BThe%20inaction%20of%20Mr.%20Naidu%20for%20the%20period%20of%20two%20months%20conveys%20that%20he%20did%20not%20believe%20that%20the%20ghee%20was%20adulterated%20physically%20with%20animal%20fats%20and%20that%20the%20finding%20of%20questionable%20quality%20was%20made%20in%20the%20process%20of%20routine%20checks%20as%20per%20the%20protocol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSir%2C%20Mr.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20a%20pathological%20and%20habitual%20liar%20has%20stooped%20so%20low%20as%20to%20seriously%20hurt%20the%20beliefs%20of%20crores%20of%20people%20purely%20for%20political%20objectives.%20His%20actions%20have%20indeed%20lowered%20not%20only%20the%20stature%20of%20a%20Chief%20Minister%20but%20also%20that%20of%20everyone%20in%20public%20life%20and%20also%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20world%20renowned%20TTD%20and%20its%20practices.%20Sir%2C%20the%20entire%20Country%20looks%20to%20you%20at%20this%20crucial%20juncture.%20It%20is%20very%20imperative%20that%20Mr.%20Naidu%20be%20reprimanded%20in%20severest%20way%20for%20his%20shameless%20act%20of%20spreading%20lies%20and%20the%20truth%20be%20brought%20to%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727263560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fubpmh698_jagan-reddy-chandrababu-naidu_625x300_07_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftirupati-laddoo-n-chandrababu-naidu-jagan-reddy-jagan-reddys-pooja-call-to-clear-chandrababu-naidus-sin-amid-laddoo-row-6646977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20has%20called%20on%20the%20people%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20pooja%20across%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20this%20Saturday%20to%20%26quot%3Batone%20for%20the%20sin%26quot%3B%20allegedly%20committed%20by%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20by%20making%20allegations%20regarding%20Tirupati%20ladoos%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftirupati-laddoo-n-chandrababu-naidu-jagan-reddy-jagan-reddys-pooja-call-to-clear-chandrababu-naidus-sin-amid-laddoo-row-6646977%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigerian%20soldier%20dismissed%20after%20alleging%20rape%20hits%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727263549000%2C%