-healthcare-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemployee%20mental%20well-being%20programmes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20fostering%20strong%20ecosystems%20and%20encouraging%20regular%20self-care%20practices%2C%20they%20are%20driving%20significant%20positive%20change%20in%20workplace%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTrue%20change%20can%20be%20created%20when%20the%20work%20culture%20focuses%20on%20people%20first.%20Companies%20should%20not%20work%20on%20employee%20engagement%20activities%20as%20some%20sort%20of%20compliance%20or%20compulsion%2C%20but%20rather%20make%20it%20a%20part%20of%20their%20overall%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Debasmita%20Sinha%2C%20chief%20psychologist%20and%20senior%20director%20%E2%80%93%20clinical%20excellence%2C%20Manah%20Wellness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManah%20Wellness%20builds%20%E2%80%9Cemotionally%20healthy%20workplaces%E2%80%9D%20by%20prioritising%20a%20%E2%80%98people-first%E2%80%99%20approach.%20As%20Debasmita%20emphasises%2C%20meaningful%20change%20starts%20from%20the%20top.%20They%20assist%20companies%20in%20creating%20strong%20policies%20that%20focus%20on%20employee%20well-being%2C%20ensuring%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20supportive%20work%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20normalised%20and%20glorified%20this%20toxic%20culture.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20employees%20to%20take%20measures%20for%20their%20own%20well-being%20by%20having%20a%20routine%20and%20focusing%20on%20self-care.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20need%20for%20mentorship%20to%20guide%20youngsters%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20stress%20and%20take%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20companies%20build%20a%20healthy%20workplace%3F%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20regular%20employee%20pulse%20checks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAsk%20questions%20and%20conduct%20surveys%20or%20focus%20group%20discussions%20to%20understand%20what%20employees%20want.%20This%20can%20help%20in%20forming%20initiatives%20and%20policies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Debasmita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConduct%20mental%20health%20screenings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInclude%20mental%20health%20screenings%20just%20like%20the%20physical%20health%20ones%20to%20determine%20who%20needs%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20people%20across%20the%20organisation%20lead%20the%20initiative%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForm%20committees%20with%20people%20from%20different%20levels%20and%20verticals.%20It%20should%20go%20beyond%20an%20HR%20engagement%20activity%2C%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrain%20your%20managers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20must%20focus%20on%20training%20and%20sensitising%20managers%2C%20says%20Advocate%20Vishakha%20Joshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20unrealistic%20deadlines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20promise%20unrealistic%20dates%20of%20delivery%20to%20your%20clients%2C%20which%20invariably%20leads%20to%20late%20nights%20and%20work%20overload.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuild%20a%20robust%20employee%20wellness%20programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalk%20to%20your%20employees%2C%20have%20team%20bonding%20sessions%20and%20open%20forums%20wherein%20employees%20can%20express%20their%20opinions%20and%20air%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%227%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20kind%20to%20each%20other%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20this%20a%20non-negotiable%20to%20ensure%20a%20happy%20workspace%20where%20employees%20and%20employers%20are%20kind%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%228%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWork%20on%20human%20capital%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMentor%20and%20coach%20employees%20and%20help%20them%20out%20when%20they%20are%20stuck.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20consider%20them%20as%20replaceable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20Debasmita%E2%80%99s%20top-down%20approach%2C%20Anu%20Singh%2C%20an%20HR%20professional%20with%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%2C%20stresses%20that%20change%20must%20begin%20at%20the%20leadership%20level.%20Anu%20%E2%80%94%20the%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EArt%20of%20Retention%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20book%20on%20how%20to%20retain%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20believes%20that%20HR%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20ensuring%20overall%20employee%20well-being%20by%20shaping%20policies%20and%20procedures%20that%20foster%20a%20healthy%20work%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20work%20on%20the%20mindset%20of%20employees%20at%20a%20workplace%20and%20create%20a%20happy%20one.%20The%20cultural%20shift%20needs%20to%20happen%20right%20from%20the%20CEO.%20Create%20an%20open%20space%20and%20provide%20flexibility%20to%20employees.%20You%20need%20to%20build%20trust%20and%20patience%20over%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20ability%20to%20say%20no%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20may%20not%20have%20the%20resources%20or%20flexibility%20to%20leave%20a%20toxic%20workplace%2C%20some%20find%20the%20courage%20to%20do%20so.%20Shobhit%20Jaju%2C%20a%20chartered%20accountant%2C%20shared%20his%20own%20experience%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%2C%20detailing%20his%20time%20as%20a%20CA%20article%20assistant%20at%20EY%20during%202010-11.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20vividly%20remember%20the%20horrors%20of%20my%20eight-month-long%20stint%20with%20EY%2C%20which%20felt%20like%20a%20lifetime.%20I%20joined%20EY%20at%20the%20very%20young%20age%20of%2019%E2%80%A6On%20my%20first%20day%2C%20I%20was%20mocked%20by%20a%20senior%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20file%20documents%20properly%20and%20was%20told%20pompously%20that%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7242787469488738304%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221207%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20burnt%20out%20in%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%20my%20career%2C%20under-slept%2C%20overworked%2C%20just%20broadly%20exhausted%20with%20my%20life%E2%80%A6My%20parents%20came%20to%20my%20rescue%2C%20and%20they%20forced%20me%20out%20of%20this%2C%20by%20explaining%20how%20this%20was%20not%20normal%2C%20and%20I%20should%20do%20a%20normal%20internship%20and%20concentrate%20more%20on%20my%20studies%2C%20not%20burn%20myself%20out%20so%20early%20in%20my%20career.%20I%20feel%20I%20was%20lucky%20as%20I%20was%20staying%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20and%20they%20could%20see%20what%20I%20was%20going%20through%2C%20guided%20me%2C%20and%20could%20not%20let%20me%20continue%20with%20something%20unsustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20completed%20his%20articleship%20in%20a%20smaller%20firm%2C%20and%20is%20today%20an%20associate%20vice%20president%20%E2%80%93%20governance%20research%20at%20Institutional%20Shareholder%20Services%20(ISS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20Shobhit%2C%20Vishakha%20Joshi%2C%20an%20advocate%2C%20had%20unpleasant%20experiences%20during%20her%20stint%20at%20one%20of%20the%20Big%20Four%20accounting%20firms.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Prospero%20Legal%20Services%2C%20where%20she%20ensures%20that%20her%20employees%20are%20treated%20fairly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20is%20meeting%20unrealistic%20deadlines%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316087%2Fassam-couple-helps-rural-northeast-india-access-affordable-mental-healthcare-mita%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleads%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20overwork%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20a%20boss%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20our%20duty%20to%20set%20realistic%20deadlines%20and%20explain%20to%20the%20client%20why%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20possible%20before%20that.%20The%20nature%20of%20legal%20work%20is%20usually%20urgent%2C%20but%20unless%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20life%20and%20death%20situation%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it%20in%20a%20decent%20frame%20of%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20planning%20leaves%20in%20advance%2C%20she%20ensures%20smooth%20operations%20while%20prioritising%20employee%20comfort.%20She%20also%20conducts%20POSH%20(Prevention%20of%20Sexual%20Harassment)%20training%20for%20corporates%20and%20points%20out%20that%2C%20currently%2C%20there%20are%20no%20specific%20labour%20laws%20in%20India%20protecting%20white-collar%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20this%20work%20culture%20is%20a%20deep%20rooted%20cultural%20issue.%20Companies%20need%20a%20very%20hands-on%20HR%20person.%20Managers%20also%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20training%20and%20gender%20sensitisation.%20Ultimately%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20your%20employees%20to%20feel%20miserable%20and%20wait%20for%20the%20day%20to%20end.%20You%20have%20to%20respect%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20autonomy%20and%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20comfortable.%20Respect%20goes%20both%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20companies%20must%20promote%20employee%20safety%20and%20take%20pride%20in%20their%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20these%20initiatives%2C%20two%20aspects%20that%20are%20often%20lacking%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20workplaces%20are%20mentorship%20and%20kindness.%20Having%20a%20good%20mentor%20is%20crucial%20for%20success%2C%20yet%20in%20many%20large%20organisations%2C%20few%20individuals%20have%20the%20time%20or%20inclination%20to%20guide%20young%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChetna%20Israni%2C%20director%20and%20co-founder%20of%20Morning%20Star%20BrandCom%2C%20is%20a%20strong%20advocate%20for%20coaching%20and%20mentoring%20her%20staff%2C%20believing%20that%20these%20elements%20are%20essential%20for%20fostering%20growth%20and%20success%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-64-1725957958.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%E2%80%99s%20high%20time%20organisations%20fostered%20empathy%20and%20kindness%20as%20core%20values%20in%20their%20work%20culture.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-64-1725957958.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-64-1725957958-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-64-1725957958-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-64-1725957958-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-64-1725957958-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365304%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20high%20time%20organisations%20fostered%20empathy%20and%20kindness%20as%20core%20values%20in%20their%