ng%3E%3Cem%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20mother%20made%20a%20statement%20on%20TV%20that%20echoed%20across%20the%20country%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20crying%20tears%20of%20blood.%20What%20can%20we%20(husband%20and%20wife)%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20helplessness%20of%20the%20common%20people%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20harsh%20system%20was%20painfully%20evident.%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20were%20unable%20to%20forget%20Manjunath%20or%20what%20his%20mother%20had%20said.%20It%20was%20time%20for%20action.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20his%20parents%20may%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331304%2Fdevanshi-yadav-shaheed-ramashray-welfare-society-bareilly-acid-attack-sexual-abuse-survivor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efight%20against%20the%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%2C%20as%20a%20community%20of%20IIM%20professionals%2C%20could.%20We%20decided%20to%20harness%20this%20collective%20power%20for%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anjali%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20quickly%20contacted%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20friends%20to%20understand%20the%20case%20details.%20Learning%20that%20a%20charge%20sheet%20had%20to%20be%20filed%20within%2090%20days%20to%20prevent%20the%20accused%20from%20obtaining%20bail%2C%20they%20contacted%20SP%20Zaki%20Ahmad%2C%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20case%20and%20had%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20quick%20arrest%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20public%20outrage%20over%20the%20acquittal%20in%20the%20Jessica%20Lal%20case%20was%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20where%20the%20rich%20and%20influential%20seemed%20to%20escape%20justice.%20This%20collective%20anger%2C%20combined%20with%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20only%20intensified%20the%20calls%20for%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20outcry%20pierced%20th