0murder.%20It%20was%20likely%20that%20they%20discussed%20the%20adulteration%20at%20the%20Mittal%20petrol%20pump%20and%20that%20he%20would%20seal%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20boss%E2%80%99%20testimony%20was%20key%20to%20proving%20the%20motive.%20Manjunath%20had%20spoken%20to%20him%20for%20almost%2020%20minutes%20on%20the%20night%20of%20his%20murder%2C%20telling%20him%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20the%20petrol%20pump%20to%20collect%20evidence.%20But%20his%20boss%20denied%20receiving%20the%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anjali%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20480px)%20100vw%2C%20480px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjunath%20with%20his%20college%20friends%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104.jpeg%20480w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104-300x191.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104-150x95.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366865%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22305%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManjunath%20with%20his%20college%20friends.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20struggled%20to%20get%20him%20to%20testify.%20Until%20the%20day%20of%20the%20hearing%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20he%20would%20even%20show%20up%20to%20testify%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2023%20March%2C%202007%20%E2%80%94%20after%20a%20trial%20of%20just%2010%20months%20%E2%80%94%20the%20verdict%20was%20pronounced%2C%20finding%20all%20eight%20accused%20guilty%20of%20murder.%20The%20main%20accused%2C%20Pawan%20Kumar%20Mittal%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20death%2C%20while%20the%20seven%20others%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20now%20sleep%20in%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20were%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20mother%E2%80%99s%20words%20after%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20couple%20fought%20the%20case%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecuring%20justice%20was%20far%20from%20easy%2C%20and%20involved%20humongous%20efforts%20from%20the%20duo%20and%20the%20volunteers%20of%20the%20trust.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20ensured%20a%20fast-tracked%20trial%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETips%20to%20Fight%20a%20Court%20Case%20%26amp%3B%20Get%20Justice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20a%20good%20lawyer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20contacts%2C%20the%20couple%20got%20a%20committed%2C%20skilled%2C%20and%20knowledgeable%20lawyer.%20According%20to%20the%20couple%2C%20having%20a%20senior%20lawyer%20who%20was%20completely%20committed%20to%20the%20case%20was%20a%20game-changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20media%20attention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20case%20stayed%20in%20the%20spotlight.%20So%2C%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20met%20with%20editors%20from%20various%20media%20organisations%2C%20who%20supported%20them%20by%20consistently%20reporting%20on%20the%20case.%20Anjali%20particularly%20mentions%20The%20Indian%20Express%20%E2%80%94%20who%20sent%20a%20reporter%20for%20every%20hearing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuild%20pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20made%20sure%20the%20hearings%20weren%E2%80%99t%20delayed%20by%20getting%20letters%20from%20influential%20people%20like%20Narayana%20Murthy%20and%20Kris%20Gopalakrishnan%20of%20Infosys%20and%20senior%20IIM%20alumni%2C%20which%20they%20sent%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20present%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20hearing%2C%20either%20Jaishankar%20or%20Anjali%20would%20travel%20from%20Mysuru%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%20They%20would%20post%20the%20hearing%20dates%20in%20online%20alumni%20groups%3B%20alumni%20who%20were%20free%20on%20the%20date%2C%20would%20also%20attend.%20A%20group%20of%20IIM%20Lucknow%20student%20volunteers%20took%20turns%20to%20be%20present%20at%20the%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaise%20funds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20their%20extensive%20network%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20funds%20for%20all%20the%20legal%20and%20travel%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENever%20give%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20despite%20the%20fight%20being%20solitary%20and%20difficult%2C%20they%20never%20lost%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20travelled%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20at%20least%2010%20times%20during%20the%20trial.%20Their%20journey%20involved%20taking%20a%20bus%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi%2C%20then%20to%20Lucknow%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20cab%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20pushed%20them%20to%20fight%20for%20a%20boy%20they%20had%20never%20met%3F%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20they%20ever%20feel%20bogged%20down%3F%20%E2%80%9CCertainly.%20Some%20days%20were%20tough.%20At%20times%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20an%20impossible%20task.%20We%20were%20carrying%20a%20heavy%20responsibility%20that%20we%20had%20to%20fulfil.%20We%20had%20to%20give%20our%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anjali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20IIM%20alumni%20volunteers%2C%20various%20people%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20strangers%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20in%20and%20helped%2C%20which%20was%20a%20major%20support%2C%20they%20say.%20To%20honour%20his%20memory%2C%20on%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20first%20death%20anniversary%2C%20the%20trust%20inaugurated%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Right%20To%20Information%20Act%20(RTI)%20helpline.%20The%20helpline%20ran%20for%20three%20years%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20use%20the%20act%20to%20fight%20corruption.%20They%20also%20established%20the%20Manjunath%20Shanmugam%20Integrity%20Award%20to%20honour%20individuals%20who%20fought%20against%20systemic%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20fight%20for%20justice%20continued%20until%202015%2C%20as%20the%20convicts%20appealed%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%202009%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202015.%20While%20the%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20convictions%2C%20it%20commuted%20Mittal%E2%80%99s%20death%20sentence%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20upheld%20the%20convictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Believe%20that%20the%20system%20works%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20immersing%20yourself%20in%20a%20case%20like%20this%20for%20so%20long%2C%20life%20changes.%20One%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20towards%20life%20evolves%2C%20and%20for%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20it%20was%20no%20different.%20While%20they%20had%20always%20been%20straightforward%20people%2C%20this%20experience%20made%20them%20even%20more%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201